roleset.name: having a normal volume of bodily fluids

role.descr: entity with a normal volume of fluids

example.name: arg1
example.text: If her pressures continue to be elevated , I would restart her ACE - inhibitor ; and ongoing evaluation of her volume status would seem to indicate she is euvolemic .
